  "body": "<!--\r\nNOTE:\r\n- General questions should go to the discord chat instead of the issue tracker.\r\n-->\r\n\r\nIn order to get more people interested in Eth2.0 in general but specially in strengthening its security it would be great to prepare a simple tutorial to modify Lodestar into an attack node to demonstrate a simple vulnerability. The vulnerability could also be manually introduced in the tutorial as part of the exercise.\r\n\r\nA goal would be to show that Eth2.0 is accessible to Typescript developers, and become a fun entry-point for those more advanced users wanting to get into the rabbit hole\r\n",
